  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE GAME:</strong></h2>In LoBlocks, the player must destroy all blocks to go to the next level. But to do it, you should solve a lot of challenging puzzle matching colors and amount of blocks with the same color.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2>- 50 challenging levels;<br>- 2 game modes (Arcade and classic with levels);<br>- Ranking online for arcade mode;<br>- Relaxing atmosphere;<br>- Authorial soundtrack in LoFi style;<br>- Pixel art;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697810/extras/c8d4ba0218ae5105d0dda24077412963.avif?t=1672702366\" width=616 height=250 /></span>",
